# 26.12.2025: Former President Ram Nath Kovind pays tributes to Sahibzada Zorawar Singh and Sahibzada Fateh Singh at Maharashtra Lok Bhavan

**Publish Date :December 26, 2025**

---

Former President Ram Nath Kovind pays tributes to Sahibzada Zorawar Singh and Sahibzada Fateh Singh at Maharashtra Lok Bhavan

Former President of India Ram Nath Kovind today paid floral tributes to the portrait of Sahibzada Zorawar Singh and Sahibzada Fateh Singh on the occasion of ‘Veer Bal Diwas’ at Maharashtra Lok Bhavan, Mumbai on Friday (26th  Dec).

The former President is on a 3 day visit to Mumbai.

content:
# 26.12.2025: Tributes paid to Sahibzada Zorawar Singh and Sahibzada Fateh Singh

**Publish Date :December 26, 2025**

---

Tributes paid to Sahibzada Zorawar Singh and Sahibzada Fateh Singh

Floral tributes were offered to the portrait of Sahibzada Zorawar Singh and Sahibzada Fateh Singh on the occasion of ‘Veer Bal Diwas’ at Maharashtra Lok Bhavan, Mumbai on Friday (26th  Dec).

Secretary to the  Governor  Dr  Prashant  Narnaware,  Comptroller of Governor’s Household Dr Nishikant Deshpande, ADC to the Governor Lt.  Vikram Kumar, officers and staff of Maharashtra Lok Bhavan offered floral tributes to Sahibzada Zorawar Singh and Sahibzada Fateh Singh  on the occasion.
